data.description: FHA 2.875% Assumable interest rate available !!!!!!!Welcome to your wonderful happy place and call it home . This 1.5 story home has been proudly and well taken care of . Three bedrooms are located downstairs including master bedroom as well as the office which french doors for privacy. Upstairs has a huge game room and a full bathroom  which can can be used as private bedroom if needed. Otherwise it is a wonderful game room. Living space opens to the kitchen but separated and dinning is off the kitchen making perfect use of the space. Stepping to the backyard, you are welcomed by humongous neighborhood playground not to mention a wonderful outdoor kitchen, a grill and a fridge perfect for bbq days with friends and family. Come see it in person to see the wonderful homey feeling . Has solar that buyer will need to take over.
